<HEADLINE> Zimbabwe Upholds "One China" Policy </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HARARE, July 30 (Xinhua) -- Zimbabwe's Deputy Foreign Minister
Nicholas Goche said Friday that his country's "One China" policy
has not changed.
</P>
<P>
"We recognize only one China, the People's Republic of China.
The remarks by the so-called President of Taiwan should be
condemned because there is no way to have two Chinas."
</P>
<P>
