Goche told Xinhua at a reception held by the Chinese embassy in
Harare to celebrate the 72nd anniversary of the establishment of
the Chinese People's Liberation Army.
</P>
<P>
Zimbabwe believes that Taiwan has always been a part of China,
it can never be recognized as a state, but a province of the
People's Republic of China, he said.  
