<HEADLINE> No Explanation Can Cover up Aim of "Two States" (2) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"We persistently advocate that we will realize the
reunification of the motherland by peaceful means. In the course
of negotiations, the two sides should negotiate on matters of
reunification on an equal footing under the 'one China' principle,
" the article said.
</P>
<P>
To terminate the state of separation between the two sides of
the Taiwan Straits and achieve the goal of reunification is the
sacred historical mission and unremitting pursuit of the Chinese
people. Two generations of CPC leadership, headed by Deng Xiaoping
and Jiang Zemin, have made unremitting efforts to seriously
implement peaceful reunification and the "one country, two systems
" policies.
</P>
<P>
"There is only one China in the world and the status of Taiwan
as a part of China remains unchanged. China's sovereignty and
territorial integrity brook no separation," the article stressed.
</P>
<P>
In an attempt to split China, Lee Teng-hui attacks the "one
China" policy without restraint.
