<HEADLINE> Hakkinen Gains Pole Position for German Grand Prix </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BERLIN, July 31 (Xinhua) -- Defending champion Mika Hakkinen of
Finland captured the pole position for the German Grand prix after
edging Heinz-Harald Frentzen in the final qualifying session at
Hockenheim on Saturday.
</P>
<P>
