</P>
<P>
China and Portugal reached an agreement here Wednesday on the
establishment of the Portuguese consulate general in the Macao
Special Administrative Region (SAR).
</P>
<P>
According to the agreement, Portugal will set up the consulate
general in the Macao SAR on December 20, 1999. 
