been terminated because he was "disagreeable and not because of
incompetence."
</P>
<P>
"After talking to national team players after the Copa America,
the association has decided to rescind the contract with Ever Hugo
Almeida," association official Guillermo Battilana said.
</P>
<P>
However, Almeida said he was suprised by the announcement and
denied he had been brusk with players.
</P>
<P>
"The association directors lie when they say there were
relationship problems because I didn't mistreat anybody," he said.
</P>
<P>
"I'm happy by the fact that they released me because I was
disagreeable as opposed to being ineffective. Since I took over in
January, we have played 14 games. We won eight, tied four, and
lost two." 
